  <title>Create minimum maximum value range
    <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20170126T172952+0100" comment="This task is the same as in Data Quality seciton.
Must be single-source!!"?>manually<?oxy_comment_end?>
  </title>
  <para>
    <screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata align="center" fileref="resources/images/data_quality/set_min_max_manually.png"
            format="PNG" width="30%"/>
        </imageobject>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
  </para>
  <orderedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>In the <emphasis role="bold">Data
          <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20170109T144747+0100" comment="Can you do it in any other app too?

SME: no" flag="done"?>Entry<?oxy_comment_end?></emphasis>
        app, open a data entry form.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20170109T150432+0100" comment="Reword"?>
      <para>Double-click the field for which you want to set the minimum maximum value range.</para>
      <?oxy_comment_end?>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>Enter <emphasis role="bold">Min limit</emphasis> and <emphasis role="bold">Max
          limit</emphasis>.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">Save</emphasis>.</para>
      <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20170109T150509+0100" comment="Reword." flag="done"?>
      <para>If values don't fall within the new value range the next time you enter data, the data
        entry cell will appear with an orange background. </para>
      <?oxy_comment_end?>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>(Optional) Type a comment to explain the reason for the discrepancy,
        f<?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20170109T150522+0100" comment="At next revision: Add better example" flag="done"?>or
        example an event at a facility which may have generated a large number of
        clients.<?oxy_comment_end?></para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>(Optional) Click <emphasis role="bold">Save comment</emphasis>.</para>
    </listitem>
  </orderedlist>
  <para>
    <tip>
      <para>Click the star icon to mark the value for further follow-up.</para>
    </tip>
  </para>
</section>
